00:47:14.630 --> 00:47:15.630
Michael: Sure.

00:47:15.630 --> 00:47:21.140
&gt;&gt; I have a question -- you may have covered
earlier in your speech but I guess it

00:47:21.140 --> 00:47:25.610
has to do a little bit about perception. I
think there are a lot of things with

00:47:25.610 --> 00:47:29.570
leadership that people take the boxes and
they're supposed to do this and they're supposed

00:47:29.570 --> 00:47:37.361
to do that. Umm, and I think sometimes, you
know, we talk about in [inaudible], that people

00:47:37.361 --> 00:47:42.950
confuse being liked with being seen as leaders.
So the disrespect factor. Uh, can

00:47:42.950 --> 00:47:47.460
you comment on that and how -- how people
sometimes get those two confused?

00:47:47.460 --> 00:47:51.570
Michael: Yeah. I think -- I think there are
a lot of reasons you need courage

00:47:51.570 --> 00:47:55.410
to be a leader, one of the things is you have
to tell -- you have to sometimes give people

00:47:55.410 --> 00:48:01.350
who work for you or with you some tough love
and, umm, often not met with great

00:48:01.350 --> 00:48:06.430
popularity. So I think it's -- I think it's
important for people to respect you

00:48:06.430 --> 00:48:10.130
and your values. I think it's important to
treat people with dignity and

00:48:10.130 --> 00:48:14.940
civility. But I don't think that's the same
thing as being popular, or well liked,

00:48:14.940 --> 00:48:17.820
because being a leader means you sometimes
have to make some tough calls on

00:48:17.820 --> 00:48:21.500
people, you have to give them some tough messages.
Now, how you give them those

00:48:21.500 --> 00:48:27.220
messages I think is important but I don't
think that leadership has anything to

00:48:27.220 --> 00:48:33.060
do with popularity in a sense that you asked
the question. In fact, it often

00:48:33.060 --> 00:48:36.800
takes -- it's -- it's often as difficult to
give people -- it's often as hurtful

00:48:36.800 --> 00:48:40.980
to tell people what they're not doing well,
as it is for the person to hear it, that

00:48:40.980 --> 00:48:44.290
they're not doing well. So I don't think leadership's
about popularity. I'm

00:48:44.290 --> 00:48:47.680
not suggesting you need to be a shrink. I'm
not suggesting you need to loan

00:48:47.680 --> 00:48:49.700
them money. What I do think is you need to
tell people the truth. It's a great

00:48:49.700 --> 00:48:51.320
question. Yes, sir?

